DIGITAL NAUTICAL PUBLICATIONS.
1. THE 94TH EDITION OF THE NGA NAUTICAL
   PUBLICATIONS-QUARTERLY UPDATE, FOURTH
   QUARTER 2009 IS MISSING THE FOLLOWING FILES:
   A. FLEET GUIDES (ATLANTIC AND PACIFIC).
   B. THE ONI MODU 101 HANDBOOK.
2. CURRENT COPIES OF THESE FILES CAN BE FOUND ON
   THE 93RD EDITION. ADDITIONALLY, FLEET GUIDES
   CAN BE DOWNLOADED FROM THE FOLLOWING WEBSITES:
   A. JWICS:
      HTTP:WWW.GEOINT.NGA.IC.GOV/PRODUCTS/DNC1/
  B. SIPRNET: 
      HTTP://WWW.GEOINT.NGA.SMIL.MIL/PRODUCTS/
      DNC1/SAILDIRECT/SAILDIRECT.HTM. 
3. THE ONI MODU 101 HANDBOOK CAN BE FOUND ON
   SIPRNET: WWW.GEOINT.NGA.SMIL.MIL/PRODUCTS/
            DNC1/MARIGIS.PHP.
4. IF CUSTOMERS REQUIRE MISSING FILES TO BE SENT
   VIA E-MAIL, A REQUEST CAN BE SUBMITTED TO THE NGA
   MARITIME CUSTOMER DATABASE AT MCDPUBS@NGA.MIL.//
